1. Any guest can view and search questions by tag, username or words.
2. Users should be able to post new questions and answers.
3. Users can flag a question, answer or comment.
4. User can upvote downvote any question, answer or comment.
5. User can add bounty to question to draw attention.
6. Moderators can close question or restore deleted questions. They can also delete answers.
7. System should send notification when someone answers their asked question.
8. Users can earn badges for their helpful answers.
9. system should indentify most frequently used tags in question.
10. user can add tag to their question.
